e public to use. <b>Everyone is welcome to use the library\'s resources for research purposes and learn about the everyday people who worked to create changes in the community.</b>\r\n\r\nThe library is publicly funded by the community. If you support our cause, you can click <strong><a href=\"https://operationscl.000webhostapp.com/donate\">here</a></strong> to donate.','About Us','','publish','closed','closed','','about-us','','','2018-04-27 17:05:28','2018-04-28 00:05:28','',0,'https://operationscl.000webhostapp.com/?page_id=49',0,'page','',0),(50,4,'2018-02-02 02:19:18','2018-02-02 02:19:18','blah','About us page','','inherit','closed','closed','','49-revision-v1','','','2018-02-02 02:19:18','2018-02-02 02:19:18','',49,'https://operationscl.000webhostapp.com/2018/02/49-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(52,4,'2018-02-02 02:23:59','2018-02-02 02:23:59','<p><iframe style=\"border: 0;\" src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3308.330909282929!2d-118.29351458478675!3d33.98403318062457!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x80c2c82f7ca60b59%3A0xe636e5d1fbe64ad6!2sSouthern+California+Library!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1523608037932\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p><p>The Library is located at<strong> 6120 S. Vermont Avenue, Los Angeles, CA 90044</strong> (off the I-110 Freeway, exit Gage). See this <a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps?q=6120+S+Vermont+Ave,+Los+Angeles,+CA&amp;hl=en&amp;sll=34.020479,-118.411732&amp;sspn=0.738704,1.036835&amp;oq=6120+S.+Vermon&amp;hnear=6120+S+Vermont+Ave,+Los+Angeles,+California+90044&amp;t=m&amp;z=16\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">map and directions</a> to the Library. If you need additional help finding the Library, please email us at <a href=\"mailto:archives@socallib.org\">archives@socallib.org</a> or call us at (323) 759-6063.</p><p>Street parking is available in front of the Library and on side streets.</p><h2>Public Transportation</h2><p>We\'re accessible by MTA Bus 204, Express Bus 754,  the Dash Southeast bus, and Metro Expo Line 806. For more information, go to the <a href=\"http://www.ladottransit.com/plantrip.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">L.A. DOT trip planner.</a></p><h2>Driving Directions</h2><p><strong>San Fernando Valley/Hollywood </strong>: Take CA-170 S/Hollywood Fwy. Merge onto US-101 S/Hollywood Fwy<strong>.</strong> Take the I-110 S/Harbor Fwy, exit toward San Pedro<strong>. </strong>Merge onto CA-110 S/Harbor Fwy. Take the exit toward Gage Ave<strong>.</strong> Turn right onto W. Gage Ave. Turn right onto S. Vermont Ave. The Library will be on the right.</p><p><strong>Santa Monica/Westside</strong>: Take the  I-10 E towards Los Angeles. Take the I-110 S exit, toward San Pedro. Merge onto CA-110 S/Harbor Fwy. Take the exit toward Gage Ave<strong>.</strong> Turn right onto W. Gage Ave. Turn right onto S. Vermont Ave. The Library will be on the right.</p><p><strong>Pasadena/Northeast:</strong> Take the N. Arroyo Pkwy  and merge onto CA-110 S/Harbor Fwy. Take the exit toward Gage Ave<strong>.</strong> Turn right onto W. Gage Ave. Turn right onto S. Vermont Ave. The Library will be on the right.</p><p><strong>San Gabriel Valley</strong>: Take the CA-60 W<strong>. </strong>Merge onto  I-10 West . Take the I-110 S exit, toward San Pedro. Merge onto CA-110 S/Harbor Fwy. Take the exit toward Gage Ave<strong>.</strong> Turn right onto W. Gage Ave. Turn right onto S. Vermont Ave. The Library will be on the right.</p><p><strong>Harbor Area:</strong>. Take the I-405 N. Take the I-110 N exit, toward Los Angeles. Take the exit toward Gage Ave<strong>.</strong> Turn left onto W. Gage Ave. Turn right onto S. Vermont Ave. The Library will be on the right.</p>','Location','','publish','closed','closed','','location','','','2018-04-18 23:21:42','2018-04-19 06:21:42','',0,'https://operationscl.000webhostapp.com/?page_id=52',0,'page','',0),(53,4,'2018-02-02 02:23:59','2018-02-02 02:23:59'