socallib.org\">archives@socallib.org</a> or call us at (323) 759-6063.</p><p>Street parking is available in front of the Library and on side streets.</p><h2>Public Transportation</h2><p>We\'re accessible by MTA Bus 204, Express Bus 754,  the Dash Southeast bus, and Metro Expo Line 806. For more information, go to the <a href=\"http://www.ladottransit.com/plantrip.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">L.A. DOT trip planner.</a></p><h2>Driving Directions</h2><p><strong>San Fernando Valley/Hollywood </strong>: Take CA-170 S/Hollywood Fwy. Merge onto US-101 S/Hollywood Fwy<strong>.</strong> Take the I-110 S/Harbor Fwy, exit toward San Pedro<strong>. </strong>Merge onto CA-110 S/Harbor Fwy. Take the exit toward Gage Ave<strong>.</strong> Turn right onto W. Gage Ave. Turn right onto S. Vermont Ave. The Library will be on the right.</p><p><strong>Santa Monica/Westside</strong>: Take the  I-10 E towards Los Angeles. Take the I-110 S exit, toward San Pedro. Merge onto CA-110 S/Harbor Fwy. Take the exit toward Gage Ave<strong>.</strong> Turn right onto W. Gage Ave. Turn right onto S. Vermont Ave. The Library will be on the right.</p><p><strong>Pasadena/Northeast:</strong> Take the N. Arroyo Pkwy  and merge onto CA-110 S/Harbor Fwy. Take the exit toward Gage Ave<strong>.</strong> Turn right onto W. Gage Ave. Turn right onto S. Vermont Ave. The Library will be on the right.</p><p><strong>San Gabriel Valley</strong>: Take the CA-60 W<strong>. </strong>Merge onto  I-10 West . Take the I-110 S exit, toward San Pedro. Merge onto CA-110 S/Harbor Fwy. Take the exit toward Gage Ave<strong>.</strong> Turn right onto W. Gage Ave. Turn right onto S. Vermont Ave. The Library will be on the right.</p><p><strong>Harbor Area:</strong>. Take the I-405 N. Take the I-110 N exit, toward Los Angeles. Take the exit toward Gage Ave<strong>.</strong> Turn left onto W. Gage Ave. Turn right onto S. Vermont Ave. The Library will be on the right.</p>','Location','','inherit','closed','closed','','52